title: # 32 - Open Tabs with Frankenstein's Lab
description:
Today on Open Tabs I go through my internet history with Youtube stars Frankenstein’s Lab! We talk about DMX, P Diddy, The Steak King, Joe Zimmerman, Patrice O’Neal, Jay Larsen, Kimi Warner, Kirsten and Danny, flash floods, wilderness survival, Hip-Hop, and much more! 

Subscribe to Frankenstein’s Lab on Youtube here:

https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCNfFcrKoCMvZLoWcNGMcoXQ

Tickets to my “Body Shots” world tour are on sale now!

For all TOUR DATE & MERCH click HERE: http://www.bertbertbert.com
